WEBVTT

1
00:01:00.743 --> 00:01:01.607
What is it. honey?

2
00:01:02.059 --> 00:01:02.719
I am busy.

3
00:01:03.259 --> 00:01:04.109
Yes.

4
00:01:04.757 --> 00:01:05.836
What do you want to buy?

5
00:01:05.861 --> 00:01:07.736
- Hui. help me write it down.
- Okay.

6
00:01:07.761 --> 00:01:11.803
Snake wine. crocodile meat.
pangolin gallbladder.

7
00:01:12.559 --> 00:01:14.441
Are you trying to poison me?

8
00:01:14.466 --> 00:01:16.005
I'm going home
for dinner tonight.

9
00:01:16.030 --> 00:01:16.890
Okay. I have to go now.

10
00:01:20.484 --> 00:01:22.372
This place is great.

11
00:01:27.375 --> 00:01:29.244
Hui. wait here.

12
00:01:30.831 --> 00:01:31.980
It was a pleasure working with you.

13
00:01:35.503 --> 00:01:37.003
Yes!

14
00:01:37.216 --> 00:01:38.842
Everyone's coming today. huh?

15
00:01:39.237 --> 00:01:39.806
Good!

16
00:01:40.800 --> 00:01:42.467
Gucheng is fantastic place.

17
00:01:42.757 --> 00:01:44.423
Perfect for tourism development.

18
00:01:44.627 --> 00:01:45.722
We can build
amusement park here...

19
00:01:46.159 --> 00:01:47.660
...and place
two hotels on the beach.

20
00:01:47.685 --> 00:01:48.975
Of course. the casino is a must.

21
00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:50.540
Leave it to me. okay?

22
00:01:50.565 --> 00:01:51.738
Mr. Song.

23
00:01:52.504 --> 00:01:53.448
Forgive me...

24
00:01:54.145 --> 00:01:56.901
...but the project manager
has chosen Cani.

25
00:01:57.686 --> 00:01:59.894
Next time we will definitely
will work together.

26
00:02:03.320 --> 00:02:04.188
I know.

27
00:02:05.489 --> 00:02:07.489
I came just to remind you...

28
00:02:07.519 --> 00:02:09.558
...your brother-in-law has
going around spreading rumors...

29
00:02:09.584 --> 00:02:11.459
...saying that you
corrupt and money laundering.

30
00:02:13.448 --> 00:02:15.390
But don't worry.
I've caught him.

31
00:02:15.640 --> 00:02:16.989
He is now in my hands.

32
00:02:17.724 --> 00:02:19.337
Should I hand it over to the police...

33
00:02:19.911 --> 00:02:22.285
...or to you?
What do you think?

34
00:02:32.980 --> 00:02:37.563
Chief. this project is quite difficult.
to be developed.

35
00:02:38.590 --> 00:02:41.674
Song is a capable developer.

36
00:02:41.888 --> 00:02:43.595
How about we talk about
joint development?

37
00:02:43.872 --> 00:02:44.594
How?

38
00:02:45.048 --> 00:02:46.628
I can handle this alone.

39
00:02:47.453 --> 00:02:49.703
Why should you invite?
this loser?

40
00:02:55.995 --> 00:02:57.370
Who do you think you are?

41
00:02:57.502 --> 00:02:58.960
You are just an outsider.

42
00:02:59.241 --> 00:03:00.451
I could shoot you right now.

43
00:03:00.476 --> 00:03:01.989
I don't believe you.

44
00:03:02.476 --> 00:03:05.248
I will shoot you
in my head right now!

45
00:03:08.940 --> 00:03:10.356
Can you shoot or not?

46
00:03:10.381 --> 00:03:12.893
You should have shot that way.
Now I'm covered in blood.

47
00:03:12.918 --> 00:03:14.084
Do you want to work for me or not?

48
00:03:14.139 --> 00:03:15.755
Get rid of your boss's body.

49
00:03:18.873 --> 00:03:20.947
Okay. it's okay.
Clean it up.

50
00:03:20.972 --> 00:03:22.515
Clean up. and we're fine.

51
00:03:23.526 --> 00:03:24.689
Everyone knows...

52
00:03:25.307 --> 00:03:26.724
...what kind of person am I.

53
00:03:27.101 --> 00:03:27.937
I'm always involved...

54
00:03:28.460 --> 00:03:30.099
...in the business that
invalid in the past...

55
00:03:30.124 --> 00:03:31.695
...but now I
want an honest business.

56
00:03:31.924 --> 00:03:32.915
Give me a chance...

57
00:03:33.228 --> 00:03:34.686
...to produce
money honestly.

58
00:03:37.309 --> 00:03:38.392
Yes. Chief?

59
00:03:39.172 --> 00:03:39.965
Head...

60
00:03:40.949 --> 00:03:42.334
...I think Mr. Song
is our best choice.

61
00:03:42.440 --> 00:03:45.227
If you don't cooperate
and something happened in your village...

62
00:03:45.252 --> 00:03:46.835
...how can I help you?

63
00:03:48.783 --> 00:03:50.680
Okay. Follow me.

64
00:03:52.359 --> 00:03:54.027
Our village has
traditional customs...

65
00:03:54.440 --> 00:03:55.481
...worshiping sacred wood.

66
00:03:55.549 --> 00:03:57.006
After the ceremony...

67
00:03:57.036 --> 00:03:59.203
...we invite guests
to take sacred wood.

68
00:04:00.276 --> 00:04:01.652
Whoever can take it...

69
00:04:01.677 --> 00:04:04.136
...will be the guest of honor
for our village for this year.

70
00:04:04.288 --> 00:04:05.964
If you can get it...

71
00:04:06.569 --> 00:04:07.713
...I will work with you.

72
00:04:08.985 --> 00:04:09.719
Agreed.

73
00:05:03.762 --> 00:05:04.727
Mr. Song...

74
00:05:05.260 --> 00:05:06.503
...nothing is
ever took...

75
00:05:06.661 --> 00:05:08.870
...sacred wood during
more than ten years.

76
00:05:10.933 --> 00:05:12.426
- No one else wants to try?
- I.

77
00:05:22.138 --> 00:05:22.993
New person?

78
00:05:23.681 --> 00:05:24.480
What's your name?

79
00:05:25.261 --> 00:05:26.511
Zheng Zha.

80
00:06:01.245 --> 00:06:02.954
You'd better just play the guitar.

81
00:08:11.882 --> 00:08:13.327
Now I have get sacred wood...

82
00:08:13.367 --> 00:08:14.534
...Can we
sign the contract?

83
00:08:14.631 --> 00:08:17.589
Why the right to cultivate
changed to land ownership rights?

84
00:08:19.007 --> 00:08:20.365
This land is too valuable...

85
00:08:20.938 --> 00:08:22.271
...to be
your "playground".

86
00:08:22.777 --> 00:08:23.713
Leave it to me.

87
00:08:24.617 --> 00:08:25.979
The money I have
give it to you...

88
00:08:26.183 --> 00:08:27.652
...enough for you
spend a lifetime.

89
00:08:27.942 --> 00:08:29.151
You call this sincerity?

90
00:08:29.441 --> 00:08:30.605
I won't sign it.

91
00:08:31.059 --> 00:08:32.681
There is no need to discuss this further.

92
00:08:33.586 --> 00:08:35.306
Chairman. just sign it.
This is a lot of money.

93
00:08:35.331 --> 00:08:36.831
We can't fight it.

94
00:08:37.194 --> 00:08:38.986
We have lived in this land
for hundreds of years.

95
00:08:39.011 --> 00:08:40.094
This land is ours.

96
00:08:40.119 --> 00:08:41.328
We can't give it to outsiders.

97
00:08:41.711 --> 00:08:42.612
Head.

98
00:08:44.098 --> 00:08:46.020
Head!

99
00:08:46.638 --> 00:08:47.378
Head!

100
00:09:02.438 --> 00:09:04.062
Anyway. you will get
what you deserve.

101
00:09:04.375 --> 00:09:05.833
Not a penny less.

102
00:09:08.082 --> 00:09:09.791
The village head was killed today.

103
00:09:10.048 --> 00:09:12.215
He fell into the sea
while squatting in the toilet.

104
00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:13.327
His whereabouts are unknown.

105
00:09:51.602 --> 00:09:53.252
Well. today is happy day.

106
00:09:53.277 --> 00:09:54.982
Let's take a photo together
to commemorate it. Come on.

107
00:09:55.007 --> 00:09:57.849
- Come closer.
- Come on. guys.

108
00:09:58.146 --> 00:10:00.480
Let me take a photo.
Let me do it.

109
00:10:03.327 --> 00:10:05.535
One two three.

110
00:10:07.052 --> 00:10:09.262
Darling. everything is fine.
I'm going home.

111
00:10:09.566 --> 00:10:10.980
Everything went smoothly.
Is the soup ready?

112
00:10:12.027 --> 00:10:14.060
A very tiring day.
I will definitely eat soup.

113
00:10:16.196 --> 00:10:19.419
10 YEARS LATER

114
00:10:19.444 --> 00:10:20.950
Kick. kick!

115
00:10:20.975 --> 00:10:23.808
Don't just stand there
and stare. kick!

116
00:10:23.901 --> 00:10:24.700
Wrong!

117
00:10:27.653 --> 00:10:28.660
Kick!

118
00:10:34.028 --> 00:10:34.846
Hello. Zha.

119
00:10:36.864 --> 00:10:38.358
I'm here.
Everything is alright.

120
00:10:38.650 --> 00:10:39.900
I will arrange it soon.

121
00:10:39.932 --> 00:10:40.932
Now...

122
00:10:42.729 --> 00:10:43.874
...you guys. come here.

123
00:10:45.904 --> 00:10:47.393
You have worked hard...

124
00:10:47.851 --> 00:10:49.293
...and now the opportunity
you become rich.

125
00:10:50.730 --> 00:10:52.229
Zha currently needs help.

126
00:10:53.221 --> 00:10:54.273
In one minute...

127
00:10:55.055 --> 00:10:56.598
...whoever
last stand...

128
00:10:56.649 --> 00:10:57.432
...we'll talk later.

129
00:11:10.187 --> 00:11:10.919
Za.

130
00:11:33.705 --> 00:11:34.969
Clean this place.

131
00:11:34.994 --> 00:11:36.380
Help them put on
bulletproof vest.

132
00:11:39.496 --> 00:11:42.299
There is money everywhere in Laika.

133
00:11:43.281 --> 00:11:45.922
If you are not afraid of death. you
have the opportunity to rise.

134
00:11:46.743 --> 00:11:48.242
From now on...

135
00:11:49.421 --> 00:11:51.254
...this is your battlefield.

136
00:11:52.548 --> 00:11:53.755
I want to see...

137
00:11:53.820 --> 00:11:55.111
...how cruel you are...

138
00:11:56.028 --> 00:11:57.280
...in order to get money.

139
00:12:31.861 --> 00:12:32.755
What's your name?

140
00:12:34.149 --> 00:12:35.046
Su Wan.

141
00:12:42.785 --> 00:12:44.222
Minister Wu. thank you.

142
00:12:44.247 --> 00:12:45.497
Thank you for coming.

143
00:12:46.539 --> 00:12:47.852
Look at the decoration of this hotel.

144
00:12:48.030 --> 00:12:51.812
Song owns eight hotels
at this level in Laika.

145
00:12:55.539 --> 00:12:56.477
Please.

146
00:12:56.748 --> 00:12:57.915
Minister Wu.

147
00:13:00.161 --> 00:13:01.622
- WELCOME.
- Mr. Song.

148
00:13:01.647 --> 00:13:02.567
Please.

149
00:13:04.893 --> 00:13:09.813
Mr. Song. you are truly a
powerful businessman in Laika.

150
00:13:10.711 --> 00:13:12.940
Considering the financial strength
and your workforce...

151
00:13:13.796 --> 00:13:16.379
...the position of mayor
you have to hold it.

152
00:13:16.818 --> 00:13:18.740
If I'm lucky enough
to become mayor...

153
00:13:19.120 --> 00:13:22.411
...I'm sure it will be
blessings to the Laika community.

154
00:13:24.851 --> 00:13:27.107
Is that girl have time tonight?

155
00:13:28.809 --> 00:13:30.620
Time is something
which can be arranged.

156
00:13:31.490 --> 00:13:33.448
As long as you like it.
that's all that matters.

157
00:13:38.897 --> 00:13:41.894
Mr. Song. everyone
think you're great.

158
00:13:42.588 --> 00:13:43.659
But as you know...

159
00:13:44.308 --> 00:13:47.059
...you are not
the only one who is capable.

160
00:13:48.199 --> 00:13:48.880
Of course.

161
00:13:50.066 --> 00:13:52.591
Have you ever heard about
transportation tycoon Lin Kun. right?

162
00:13:54.142 --> 00:13:55.392
He also wants to run for office.

163
00:13:55.690 --> 00:13:56.338
Good.

164
00:13:56.960 --> 00:13:58.597
Competition drives progress.

165
00:14:00.375 --> 00:14:01.429
This position...

166
00:14:01.834 --> 00:14:03.420
...now at 30 million dollars.

167
00:14:05.251 --> 00:14:07.563
But if Lin Kun run for office...

168
00:14:08.392 --> 00:14:13.100
...I can't say
how much it cost at that time.

169
00:14:13.185 --> 00:14:14.000
Okay.

170
00:14:15.544 --> 00:14:17.125
Thank you for the information.
Mr. Minister.

171
00:14:23.143 --> 00:14:23.837
Minister..

172
00:14:26.448 --> 00:14:27.538
Thank you for your help.

173
00:14:28.442 --> 00:14:30.282
By the way. when
talking about watches...

174
00:14:30.307 --> 00:14:31.890
...it doesn't have to
be the most expensive.

175
00:14:31.915 --> 00:14:34.449
If one day your status changes...

176
00:14:35.270 --> 00:14:37.024
...choose what suits your taste
high to wear.

177
00:14:38.518 --> 00:14:39.157
Understand.

178
00:14:42.874 --> 00:14:43.990
Enjoy.

179
00:14:47.497 --> 00:14:49.184
He doesn't like you.

180
00:14:52.260 --> 00:14:53.747
Boss. how did it go?

181
00:14:55.009 --> 00:14:59.474
As I expected.
Lin Kun also volunteered.

182
00:15:01.457 --> 00:15:02.425
Have you got what I asked for?

183
00:15:11.852 --> 00:15:13.304
I told them moving tonight.

184
00:15:16.644 --> 00:15:17.945
Let Zha take care of it.

185
00:15:19.881 --> 00:15:21.507
Send Lin Kun a big gift.

186
00:15:23.087 --> 00:15:23.844
Okay.

187
00:15:28.081 --> 00:15:32.624
LAIKA CHINA-CHINA

188
00:15:44.914 --> 00:15:45.956
I'll just go up by myself.

189
00:15:46.261 --> 00:15:47.070
Get ready and help me later.

190
00:15:53.627 --> 00:15:55.038
Let us...

191
00:15:55.804 --> 00:15:56.998
...make Laika...

192
00:15:57.548 --> 00:15:58.673
...a better place!

193
00:15:59.132 --> 00:16:00.256
Cheers!

194
00:16:03.585 --> 00:16:05.380
Would you like to make a donation?

195
00:16:07.577 --> 00:16:09.017
I came here to bring
a gift for you.

196
00:16:12.865 --> 00:16:15.634
- Apparently he is.
- She is an actress.

197
00:16:18.549 --> 00:16:21.048
I heard Mr. Lin
having an affair with that woman.

198
00:16:21.100 --> 00:16:22.474
You got her pregnant...

199
00:16:22.737 --> 00:16:24.225
...and now you want
silence him.

200
00:16:25.317 --> 00:16:26.911
Luckily. I succeeded
save him in time.

201
00:16:28.134 --> 00:16:29.367
Take my wife away first.

202
00:16:29.754 --> 00:16:31.379
Yes. sir. Mrs. Lin. let's go.

203
00:16:31.718 --> 00:16:33.342
Mrs. Lin. come.

204
00:16:34.408 --> 00:16:36.127
This phone is recording
every word you say...

205
00:16:36.189 --> 00:16:37.672
...to him during
the last three years...

206
00:16:38.614 --> 00:16:41.974
...including every time you
attack him or threaten him.

207
00:16:43.874 --> 00:16:44.504
That's enough.

208
00:16:45.257 --> 00:16:46.538
Because you are happy...

209
00:16:46.807 --> 00:16:47.785
...I will not spoil
your mood.

210
00:16:48.764 --> 00:16:49.731
See you.

211
00:16:54.277 --> 00:16:55.790
Take that phone back.

212
00:16:56.486 --> 00:16:57.460
Okay sir.

213
00:17:02.347 --> 00:17:04.420
Catch him!
Take back the phone!

214
00:17:11.938 --> 00:17:14.008
Stop! Don't run!

215
00:17:14.546 --> 00:17:15.920
Stop! Don't run!

216
00:17:21.955 --> 00:17:22.886
Don't run!

217
00:17:23.533 --> 00:17:24.873
Move!

218
00:17:27.017 --> 00:17:28.140
Move!

219
00:17:30.455 --> 00:17:31.782
Don't run!

220
00:17:33.253 --> 00:17:34.461
Stop!

221
00:17:54.087 --> 00:17:54.818
Stop!

222
00:17:54.949 --> 00:17:56.140
Come on up.

223
00:18:06.563 --> 00:18:07.855
I will kill you!

224
00:18:11.958 --> 00:18:13.353
How could you be so careless?

225
00:18:13.812 --> 00:18:14.996
Get rid of this problem.

226
00:18:15.466 --> 00:18:16.914
Involve the public relations team.

227
00:18:23.713 --> 00:18:24.621
Lin Kun.

228
00:18:25.392 --> 00:18:27.033
You don't have to be so cruel.

229
00:19:24.427 --> 00:19:26.135
You are known now.

230
00:19:27.407 --> 00:19:28.718
You still want to
running for mayor?

231
00:19:29.310 --> 00:19:30.476
Just step back.

232
00:19:31.800 --> 00:19:34.020
I can also promise to you now...

233
00:19:34.539 --> 00:19:35.860
...that you can stay in business.

234
00:19:36.951 --> 00:19:38.067
I even give you resources.

235
00:19:41.987 --> 00:19:42.507
Cheers.

236
00:19:44.424 --> 00:19:45.057
What?

237
00:19:45.348 --> 00:19:49.780
You think you can use
one woman to force me out?

238
00:19:50.745 --> 00:19:52.740
You underestimate me.

239
00:19:55.078 --> 00:19:56.860
This is a private place.

240
00:19:58.058 --> 00:19:59.107
Let them all go.

241
00:20:00.273 --> 00:20:01.167
Don't you want a drink?

242
00:20:01.729 --> 00:20:04.145
Then I will use it
to respect you.

243
00:20:13.547 --> 00:20:15.338
I changed my mind.

244
00:20:16.134 --> 00:20:17.676
People like you...

245
00:20:18.972 --> 00:20:20.888
...will ultimately be punished.

246
00:20:31.486 --> 00:20:35.060
Either you die or he does.

247
00:20:35.432 --> 00:20:36.780
Just choose.

248
00:20:53.923 --> 00:20:55.585
<i>Hui. are you done?</i>

249
00:20:56.061 --> 00:20:56.780
Okay.

250
00:20:58.267 --> 00:20:59.244
Stop fighting.

251
00:20:59.624 --> 00:21:00.442
Time to go.

252
00:21:09.918 --> 00:21:11.525
Let's go. There's a police officer.

253
00:21:11.550 --> 00:21:12.480
Don't mind me.

254
00:21:27.769 --> 00:21:28.719
Let's go.

255
00:21:29.737 --> 00:21:30.894
You want to kill him?

256
00:21:37.646 --> 00:21:38.646
Put down your weapons!

257
00:21:40.071 --> 00:21:41.880
Hey. put down your knife!

258
00:21:43.377 --> 00:21:44.046
Let go!

259
00:21:44.515 --> 00:21:45.599
Drop it.

260
00:21:46.347 --> 00:21:47.347
Drop the knife!

261
00:21:48.325 --> 00:21:49.099
Now!

262
00:21:50.224 --> 00:21:51.181
Handcuff them and take them all away.

263
00:21:54.463 --> 00:21:58.702
LAIKA POLICE STATION

264
00:22:09.691 --> 00:22:11.107
Did I tell you to?
to drink it?

265
00:22:22.558 --> 00:22:23.558
Pack.

266
00:22:25.807 --> 00:22:27.367
Have you vented your frustration?

267
00:22:27.836 --> 00:22:29.169
Isn't it time to let go?

268
00:22:29.998 --> 00:22:32.447
You can't hold us long
for group disputes.

269
00:22:35.608 --> 00:22:36.847
Lin Kun is dead.

270
00:22:39.722 --> 00:22:41.805
Are you the one fishing?
to keep its members away...

271
00:22:42.230 --> 00:22:43.707
...so Song Bang can attack?

272
00:22:44.804 --> 00:22:45.487
What?

273
00:22:47.160 --> 00:22:49.672
You mean Song Bang kill Lin Kun?

274
00:22:50.645 --> 00:22:51.820
Do you have any witnesses?

275
00:22:55.211 --> 00:22:57.666
You can come to us
when you have proof.

276
00:23:05.454 --> 00:23:07.420
Song Bang wants to run
himself to become mayor.

277
00:23:08.031 --> 00:23:09.580
You must have big plans.

278
00:23:11.587 --> 00:23:13.212
But. I have a message for him!

279
00:23:13.337 --> 00:23:14.545
As long as I'm alive...

280
00:23:14.570 --> 00:23:16.247
...I will monitor
all of you!

281
00:23:17.274 --> 00:23:18.053
Mr. Mai.

282
00:23:19.743 --> 00:23:22.380
I also want to say this
on behalf of Mr. Song...

283
00:23:23.323 --> 00:23:26.314
...that with your position.
you don't need to worry.

284
00:23:26.842 --> 00:23:31.320
If I were you.
I will retire in peace.

285
00:23:31.780 --> 00:23:32.686
That's great. isn't it?

286
00:23:35.298 --> 00:23:36.969
You're just a trash mafia!

287
00:23:36.994 --> 00:23:37.994
Come on! Hit me!

288
00:23:38.204 --> 00:23:40.153
I will not stop
watching over you guys!

289
00:23:40.459 --> 00:23:41.300
What are you doing?

290
00:23:42.943 --> 00:23:44.180
Aren't you
Have you complained enough?

291
00:23:49.544 --> 00:23:51.419
You are a law enforcer.

292
00:23:52.104 --> 00:23:53.686
Control yourself.

293
00:24:01.342 --> 00:24:02.254
You may go.

294
00:24:02.599 --> 00:24:03.660
There is someone who guarantees you.

295
00:24:11.429 --> 00:24:12.857
Absolutely impatient.

296
00:24:13.623 --> 00:24:14.707
How to
can you catch the criminal?

297
00:24:28.631 --> 00:24:29.380
Pack.

298
00:24:32.431 --> 00:24:35.380
You've done a lot.
and many people are watching you.

299
00:24:36.363 --> 00:24:38.147
You have to be careful.

300
00:24:43.279 --> 00:24:45.112
Thanks for the warning.
Officer Luo.

301
00:25:12.268 --> 00:25:14.060
Still pretending
even though you almost died.

302
00:25:20.043 --> 00:25:20.801
Adultery.

303
00:25:30.864 --> 00:25:31.753
I'll call Xiaodao.

304
00:25:31.778 --> 00:25:32.778
Come in.

305
00:25:39.002 --> 00:25:40.854
Zha. are you okay?

306
00:25:43.444 --> 00:25:44.753
What happened?

307
00:25:45.201 --> 00:25:46.201
You are badly injured.

308
00:25:47.789 --> 00:25:49.493
They all said
you have mystical abilities.

309
00:25:49.915 --> 00:25:52.794
Others will not survive.

310
00:25:53.208 --> 00:25:55.400
But. you still look cool
and sit in style.

311
00:25:56.002 --> 00:25:56.807
Where's the morphine?

312
00:25:57.183 --> 00:25:58.725
I'm here and everything will be safe.

313
00:25:59.340 --> 00:26:00.047
Morphine.

314
00:26:01.820 --> 00:26:03.069
Stitches.

315
00:26:06.166 --> 00:26:06.928
No need.

316
00:26:07.641 --> 00:26:08.455
No anesthetic?

317
00:26:08.480 --> 00:26:09.743
If you keep moving.
I can't sew properly.

318
00:26:09.768 --> 00:26:10.975
I can do it myself.

319
00:26:20.379 --> 00:26:21.671
Alone?

320
00:26:23.462 --> 00:26:24.546
Doesn't that hurt?

321
00:26:25.110 --> 00:26:26.502
Since birth I have been insensitive
in pain.

322
00:26:27.371 --> 00:26:29.393
So. if your hand is cut off.
won't you get sick?

323
00:26:29.625 --> 00:26:30.667
There is no pain.

324
00:26:32.337 --> 00:26:33.961
Just uncomfortable.

325
00:26:37.164 --> 00:26:38.456
Zha. I'm going.

326
00:26:38.494 --> 00:26:39.494
I can't take it anymore.

327
00:26:56.014 --> 00:26:59.325
When the police came here.
I told you to stop.

328
00:27:00.225 --> 00:27:01.249
Why don't you stop?

329
00:27:08.316 --> 00:27:09.542
I want to kill him.

330
00:27:13.439 --> 00:27:16.293
If I don't kill them.
they will kill me.

331
00:27:16.873 --> 00:27:18.060
Now you're a gang member.

332
00:27:18.823 --> 00:27:19.900
Not a killer.

333
00:27:21.830 --> 00:27:23.107
If you keep thinking
to kill people...

334
00:27:23.745 --> 00:27:25.287
...sooner or later
you will be killed.

335
00:27:34.105 --> 00:27:37.397
So. Zha. what should I do?

336
00:27:38.391 --> 00:27:39.807
Let them kill me?

337
00:27:41.966 --> 00:27:44.757
This is my restaurant. not your company.

338
00:27:45.545 --> 00:27:47.420
Don't talk about that here.

339
00:27:48.978 --> 00:27:50.727
Zheng Zha. can we talk upstairs?

340
00:27:59.500 --> 00:28:02.567
This is the first and last time.

341
00:28:04.323 --> 00:28:05.587
If you ignore my orders again...

342
00:28:06.500 --> 00:28:07.681
...I will get you out.

343
00:28:22.482 --> 00:28:23.940
Su Wan is quite special.

344
00:28:25.333 --> 00:28:26.402
Special problem.

345
00:28:27.247 --> 00:28:28.280
Special like you.

346
00:28:29.929 --> 00:28:31.220
Why is he like me?

347
00:28:31.820 --> 00:28:33.107
I'm much more handsome.

348
00:29:29.602 --> 00:29:31.269
No change.

349
00:30:03.121 --> 00:30:03.742
Lai.

350
00:30:04.829 --> 00:30:06.954
You are the best chemist
that I know.

351
00:30:07.368 --> 00:30:09.326
You helped me
make a lot of money.

352
00:30:10.320 --> 00:30:12.100
You said you wanted to go out...

353
00:30:12.372 --> 00:30:14.180
...and I let you go
without saying anything.

354
00:30:14.899 --> 00:30:16.067
Now I have a little problem.

355
00:30:16.328 --> 00:30:17.633
I need a lot of money.

356
00:30:20.404 --> 00:30:24.273
I don't think you'll refuse. right?

357
00:30:25.517 --> 00:30:29.279
But once. you promised me...

358
00:30:30.760 --> 00:30:32.606
...to never look for me again.

359
00:30:38.873 --> 00:30:42.280
Okay. forget what I said.

360
00:30:57.917 --> 00:31:01.020
This garbage compactor truck
our factory's new product.

361
00:31:02.258 --> 00:31:04.180
There's too much trash in Laika.

362
00:31:05.128 --> 00:31:07.347
I have to clean the city
for my campaign.

363
00:31:08.516 --> 00:31:09.927
I'll start with your family.

364
00:31:11.198 --> 00:31:14.129
Your brother. your sister.
your wife. and your son.

365
00:31:14.154 --> 00:31:15.154
Who's first?

366
00:31:15.646 --> 00:31:16.713
Bring the young ones.

367
00:31:17.180 --> 00:31:18.100
He is stronger.

368
00:31:18.125 --> 00:31:20.012
Lai. help me!

369
00:31:21.120 --> 00:31:21.730
Help!

370
00:31:21.755 --> 00:31:22.780
Help me. Lai!

371
00:31:23.309 --> 00:31:24.559
Please!

372
00:31:26.591 --> 00:31:27.880
Don't!

373
00:31:28.906 --> 00:31:29.954
Bro!

374
00:31:35.538 --> 00:31:37.891
Chemist Lai is a genius.

375
00:31:37.916 --> 00:31:38.631
Bro!

376
00:31:38.656 --> 00:31:40.671
Does not do anything
make you trash.

377
00:31:41.640 --> 00:31:44.082
These people change you
from genius to trash.

378
00:31:44.281 --> 00:31:45.361
That means they are more trash!

379
00:31:45.688 --> 00:31:46.896
Put them in!

380
00:31:49.025 --> 00:31:49.827
Lai!

381
00:31:51.112 --> 00:31:52.112
Don't!

382
00:31:53.410 --> 00:31:54.410
Lai!

383
00:31:54.435 --> 00:31:55.560
Darling!

384
00:31:55.604 --> 00:31:57.059
- Mother!
- Don't!

385
00:31:57.285 --> 00:31:58.868
Bro. please stop.

386
00:31:58.893 --> 00:32:00.244
Stop! I beg you!

387
00:32:00.269 --> 00:32:00.841
Bro!

388
00:32:04.025 --> 00:32:05.025
Don't!

389
00:32:05.997 --> 00:32:06.894
Don't!

390
00:32:06.919 --> 00:32:08.073
Final.

391
00:32:10.111 --> 00:32:11.111
Please!

392
00:32:11.390 --> 00:32:12.340
Father!

393
00:32:12.523 --> 00:32:14.013
Son!

394
00:32:14.474 --> 00:32:16.893
- Son!
- Father!

395
00:32:16.918 --> 00:32:17.651
Son!

396
00:32:17.676 --> 00:32:18.756
Bro! I will do it.

397
00:32:18.781 --> 00:32:22.229
Don't kill my son!
Bro. I will do it.

398
00:32:26.323 --> 00:32:27.699
Run!

399
00:32:27.811 --> 00:32:29.186
Run faster!

400
00:32:30.131 --> 00:32:31.020
Good.

401
00:32:31.421 --> 00:32:32.780
You can run.

402
00:32:42.675 --> 00:32:43.307
How is the result?

403
00:32:44.056 --> 00:32:45.427
I heard you were badly injured.

404
00:32:45.452 --> 00:32:46.189
You are okay?

405
00:32:47.135 --> 00:32:48.060
Just a small wound.

406
00:32:49.187 --> 00:32:50.226
Quickly thank Hui.

407
00:32:51.290 --> 00:32:52.623
Thank you. Hui.

408
00:33:02.129 --> 00:33:03.754
I heard you're a great fighter.

409
00:33:04.164 --> 00:33:05.373
Join us.

410
00:33:24.270 --> 00:33:25.978
Look. the fish is flying.

411
00:33:27.408 --> 00:33:29.773
He said. if the fish
jump to the surface...

412
00:33:29.798 --> 00:33:31.740
...that's because of the big fish
is chasing them.

413
00:33:32.769 --> 00:33:33.767
There is one!

414
00:33:34.995 --> 00:33:35.875
Well done. Zha!

415
00:33:35.900 --> 00:33:37.015
You caught the first one.

416
00:33:37.040 --> 00:33:38.248
Absolutely can.

417
00:33:39.385 --> 00:33:40.263
Very good!

418
00:33:40.408 --> 00:33:41.014
Good.

419
00:33:41.534 --> 00:33:43.030
I caught a big one too.

420
00:33:43.055 --> 00:33:43.959
Come on! Help me!

421
00:33:43.984 --> 00:33:46.944
Come on!

422
00:33:47.334 --> 00:33:48.486
The rod could break. right?

423
00:33:49.988 --> 00:33:51.448
You're better for this. Boss.

424
00:33:52.633 --> 00:33:56.281
You know what bait
what do I use to catch big fish?

425
00:33:57.535 --> 00:34:01.420
Everyone can catch big fish
with crab. but my bait...

426
00:34:03.887 --> 00:34:05.314
...is a small fish.

427
00:34:07.285 --> 00:34:08.060
Come on.

428
00:34:16.387 --> 00:34:18.011
You know I'm running
himself to become mayor.

429
00:34:18.915 --> 00:34:20.083
That costs a lot of money.

430
00:34:21.382 --> 00:34:23.715
I found a stranger
who wants crystal methamphetamine.

431
00:34:24.550 --> 00:34:26.133
I also have a chemist.

432
00:34:26.158 --> 00:34:27.575
But. I'm short of raw materials.

433
00:34:28.295 --> 00:34:29.295
Do you know?

434
00:34:30.004 --> 00:34:30.940
What about Lewis?

435
00:34:31.529 --> 00:34:32.740
He has a lot of raw materials.

436
00:34:33.549 --> 00:34:34.967
So true.

437
00:34:35.280 --> 00:34:36.300
He's got the goods.

438
00:34:36.600 --> 00:34:37.974
But. he also
the most expensive in town.

439
00:34:38.139 --> 00:34:40.580
No choice.
we have to buy from him.

440
00:34:48.609 --> 00:34:50.275
I will use bait
worth 1 million dollars...

441
00:34:51.389 --> 00:34:52.920
...to catch fish
worth 8 million dollars.

442
00:34:55.746 --> 00:34:56.662
Who wants to come?

443
00:35:06.576 --> 00:35:07.493
I want to.

444
00:35:11.896 --> 00:35:13.062
What's your name?

445
00:35:13.509 --> 00:35:14.406
Su Wan.

446
00:35:22.915 --> 00:35:23.860
I go.

447
00:35:27.479 --> 00:35:28.380
Follow me.

448
00:35:34.015 --> 00:35:35.860
Zha. where are we going?

449
00:35:44.795 --> 00:35:45.757
Are you looking to die?

450
00:35:46.705 --> 00:35:47.504
What?

451
00:35:52.315 --> 00:35:53.815
Do you know who Lewis is?

452
00:35:54.334 --> 00:35:55.500
He is insane.

453
00:35:55.992 --> 00:35:57.860
If you want to rob him.
then you are looking for death.

454
00:35:58.478 --> 00:35:59.940
The bait must be eaten.

455
00:36:00.813 --> 00:36:03.020
Even though the big fish was caught.
you will still die.

456
00:36:09.318 --> 00:36:10.564
I'll talk to Mr. Song.

457
00:36:11.390 --> 00:36:12.626
I will find a way
get raw materials.

458
00:36:14.449 --> 00:36:15.460
This place is not for you.

459
00:36:16.981 --> 00:36:18.260
Get out of here tonight
this is by ship.

460
00:36:19.166 --> 00:36:21.340
If you're scared. I'll go alone.

461
00:36:27.954 --> 00:36:28.740
Go.

462
00:36:29.112 --> 00:36:30.380
I am not afraid with pain.

463
00:36:34.002 --> 00:36:36.220
But. that doesn't mean
you can't die!

464
00:36:45.226 --> 00:36:46.140
Several things...

465
00:36:48.335 --> 00:36:51.420
...worth betting on.

466
00:36:53.352 --> 00:36:54.620
You never felt that?

467
00:37:19.917 --> 00:37:20.380
Come on.

468
00:37:23.391 --> 00:37:24.460
Eat it.

469
00:37:37.502 --> 00:37:38.780
What do you want for tonight?

470
00:37:39.792 --> 00:37:40.500
There isn't any.

471
00:37:41.464 --> 00:37:42.860
There is something that must be done
we do tonight.

472
00:37:46.667 --> 00:37:47.820
How about a late night snack?

473
00:37:48.320 --> 00:37:49.060
Durian pie.

474
00:37:51.086 --> 00:37:51.780
How many?

475
00:37:54.259 --> 00:37:55.635
What do you mean "how much"?

476
00:37:55.728 --> 00:37:57.300
We both will go
then come back again.

477
00:38:14.471 --> 00:38:17.820
LET'S PLAY!

478
00:40:00.582 --> 00:40:02.498
Is Mr. Song looking down on me?

479
00:40:02.549 --> 00:40:04.257
For important transactions...

480
00:40:04.449 --> 00:40:06.387
...he sent the novice that night.

481
00:40:08.362 --> 00:40:09.340
You have so much guts.

482
00:40:10.276 --> 00:40:11.820
Son.

483
00:40:15.626 --> 00:40:16.860
Drink it.

484
00:40:35.794 --> 00:40:37.027
Wait.

485
00:40:37.052 --> 00:40:37.940
Check the item first.

486
00:41:00.072 --> 00:41:02.379
<i>Boss. they
I have checked the goods.</i>

487
00:41:02.404 --> 00:41:03.947
<i>No problem.</i>

488
00:41:18.950 --> 00:41:21.407
Son. you are so brave.

489
00:41:21.432 --> 00:41:22.500
Let's have fun.

490
00:41:46.232 --> 00:41:49.780
Son. if they leave...

491
00:41:53.616 --> 00:41:55.180
...you will die too.

492
00:41:56.481 --> 00:41:57.980
Tell them to hand over the goods!

493
00:42:02.065 --> 00:42:03.340
Give them the goods.

494
00:42:05.796 --> 00:42:06.626
Give it to them.

495
00:42:07.103 --> 00:42:08.900
Okay. bring it.

496
00:42:18.842 --> 00:42:20.140
<i>Don't let them go!</i>

497
00:43:19.709 --> 00:43:21.940
You are the first person who dares
robbed my stuff.

498
00:43:23.646 --> 00:43:25.853
I will show you
what it's like to live in hell.

499
00:43:26.091 --> 00:43:27.060
Attack him!

500
00:44:00.303 --> 00:44:02.011
I thought you were gone.

501
00:44:02.926 --> 00:44:03.884
We come together.

502
00:44:04.642 --> 00:44:06.220
Also have to go together.

503
00:44:09.176 --> 00:44:11.660
There are more people who want to die.

504
00:45:12.627 --> 00:45:13.460
Za.

505
00:45:14.482 --> 00:45:16.132
This time. you do it good job.

506
00:45:16.782 --> 00:45:17.740
You have helped me a lot.

507
00:45:18.935 --> 00:45:20.395
I want to tell you something.

508
00:45:20.541 --> 00:45:21.833
At the moment...

509
00:45:21.935 --> 00:45:23.700
...I'm no longer suitable
manage the company.

510
00:45:24.476 --> 00:45:27.340
Come to the company
in the last few days.

511
00:45:27.948 --> 00:45:29.420
I will hand it over
the whole business to you.

512
00:45:30.473 --> 00:45:32.780
Next Tuesday. come with me...

513
00:45:33.948 --> 00:45:35.260
...to make transactions
with strangers.

514
00:45:37.895 --> 00:45:38.621
Boss.

515
00:45:39.532 --> 00:45:41.340
You have become
underground king Laika.

516
00:45:42.455 --> 00:45:44.220
Why do you want to enter politics?

517
00:45:47.293 --> 00:45:48.300
Do you still remember...

518
00:45:48.892 --> 00:45:50.980
...ten years ago
while at the floating market?

519
00:45:51.656 --> 00:45:52.980
If I don't deal with Terry...

520
00:45:53.448 --> 00:45:55.180
...none of us
can stand until now.

521
00:45:56.894 --> 00:45:58.660
He's just a deputy bureau chief...

522
00:45:59.039 --> 00:46:00.540
...but can determine
our fate. Why?

523
00:46:01.328 --> 00:46:02.220
Because he is...

524
00:46:02.638 --> 00:46:04.300
...who makes the rules of the game.

525
00:46:05.190 --> 00:46:06.860
Bukeya is right.

526
00:46:07.496 --> 00:46:09.371
We sat at the dining table...

527
00:46:09.516 --> 00:46:11.500
...or become a dish
at the dining table.

528
00:46:12.212 --> 00:46:13.921
Of course we want to sit...

529
00:46:13.959 --> 00:46:15.250
...and enjoy the meal
at the dining table.

530
00:46:15.275 --> 00:46:16.660
Otherwise. we become
dishes for others.

531
00:46:23.166 --> 00:46:23.980
Today...

532
00:46:26.043 --> 00:46:26.900
...you are me from the past.

533
00:46:28.502 --> 00:46:29.440
And I am...

534
00:46:31.700 --> 00:46:33.065
...your future self.

535
00:46:54.208 --> 00:46:56.254
Soon. this whole city...

536
00:46:56.578 --> 00:46:58.453
...become ours.

537
00:47:12.250 --> 00:47:13.547
What are you doing?

538
00:47:15.420 --> 00:47:16.968
You said. this place outdated.

539
00:47:18.053 --> 00:47:20.705
Because today there is time.
I came to renovate.

540
00:47:21.589 --> 00:47:22.953
This color is warm and comfortable. right?

541
00:47:25.058 --> 00:47:26.021
You changed your ways.

542
00:47:26.835 --> 00:47:28.930
Change my ways?

543
00:47:30.715 --> 00:47:31.693
Change profession.

544
00:47:32.941 --> 00:47:34.163
It turns out what you said was true.

545
00:47:35.542 --> 00:47:36.516
I've been thinking
about it for a long time.

546
00:47:38.281 --> 00:47:39.280
I don't want to live
like this again.

547
00:47:41.500 --> 00:47:42.980
I want to have a new identity.

548
00:47:44.016 --> 00:47:44.780
What's that?

549
00:47:53.082 --> 00:47:54.100
To be your husband.

550
00:48:04.719 --> 00:48:05.780
In that case...

551
00:48:06.532 --> 00:48:08.100
...I have a contract for you.

552
00:48:20.022 --> 00:48:21.140
Are you pregnant?

553
00:48:28.400 --> 00:48:29.734
- Forgive me.
- That's okay.

554
00:48:29.959 --> 00:48:32.466
Add more dishes.
Let me cook tonight.

555
00:48:32.491 --> 00:48:34.407
What do you want to eat? Come on.

556
00:48:34.663 --> 00:48:35.420
Su Wan!

557
00:48:36.205 --> 00:48:38.780
- Help me!
- <i>I'm fine.</i>

558
00:48:57.420 --> 00:48:58.812
Eat a lot.

559
00:49:04.310 --> 00:49:04.856
Hey.

560
00:49:10.400 --> 00:49:11.020
Za.

561
00:49:24.312 --> 00:49:25.740
You laugh so happily.

562
00:49:26.538 --> 00:49:27.660
Really like boats?

563
00:49:32.211 --> 00:49:33.820
This boat previously belonged to my father.

564
00:49:37.022 --> 00:49:38.500
Aren't you afraid?
does the cat have a skin disease?

565
00:49:39.022 --> 00:49:41.500
If I don't take care of it.
who else takes care of them?

566
00:49:42.791 --> 00:49:44.780
You are very fierce when you fight.

567
00:49:45.469 --> 00:49:46.300
I didn't expect that.

568
00:49:50.627 --> 00:49:51.621
I feel...

569
00:49:53.850 --> 00:49:55.860
...you don't fit in
for this job.

570
00:49:59.440 --> 00:50:01.660
Once this transaction is completed...

571
00:50:02.625 --> 00:50:06.060
...I will buy you a boat...

572
00:50:07.574 --> 00:50:10.140
...so you can get started
business honestly.

573
00:50:12.440 --> 00:50:14.540
Let's say.
that's the way out for me.

574
00:50:16.271 --> 00:50:17.919
When I can't fight anymore...

575
00:50:18.608 --> 00:50:19.780
...I will look for you.

576
00:50:20.461 --> 00:50:22.420
Right. Mr. Su?

577
00:50:23.616 --> 00:50:24.540
Thank you. Zha.

578
00:50:36.208 --> 00:50:37.780
Why are you still wearing it?
that watch?

579
00:50:38.146 --> 00:50:39.300
It looks outdated.

580
00:50:41.364 --> 00:50:42.500
Even though it's outdated...

581
00:50:43.754 --> 00:50:44.860
...this watch...

582
00:50:47.348 --> 00:50:49.180
...my father's legacy
before he died.

583
00:50:52.496 --> 00:50:53.740
I wear it...

584
00:50:55.378 --> 00:50:57.460
...to continue
reminds me...

585
00:50:59.266 --> 00:51:00.580
...so as not to forget the family.

586
00:51:10.355 --> 00:51:12.980
Zha. you are a good person.

587
00:51:16.363 --> 00:51:18.100
Good people deserve
get good things.

588
00:51:19.556 --> 00:51:20.220
This is for you.

589
00:51:20.610 --> 00:51:21.900
In particular
I ordered it for you.

590
00:52:32.375 --> 00:52:36.082
FIVE DAYS BEFORE TRANSACTION

591
00:52:41.982 --> 00:52:42.900
Za.

592
00:52:44.292 --> 00:52:48.083
FOUR DAYS BEFORE TRANSACTION

593
00:52:51.917 --> 00:52:56.083
THREE DAYS BEFORE TRANSACTION

594
00:53:05.001 --> 00:53:09.083
TWO DAYS BEFORE TRANSACTION

595
00:53:36.792 --> 00:53:40.500
TRANSACTION DAY

596
00:53:50.066 --> 00:53:52.817
Hey! Willie!

597
00:53:53.225 --> 00:53:55.140
How are you. man? Big guy. huh?

598
00:53:55.391 --> 00:53:57.527
- So. where are we going?
- I don't know.

599
00:53:57.985 --> 00:53:59.539
I'm also waiting for my boss.

600
00:54:00.082 --> 00:54:01.020
So..

601
00:54:06.630 --> 00:54:08.300
Mr. Song invites you
to get on the bus.

602
00:54:10.861 --> 00:54:12.860
Let's go.

603
00:54:34.634 --> 00:54:35.540
Hi. Willie.

604
00:54:35.814 --> 00:54:36.980
Welcome to Laika!

605
00:54:37.454 --> 00:54:38.860
The boss sends his regards to you.

606
00:54:39.529 --> 00:54:40.580
Let's see.

607
00:54:41.433 --> 00:54:42.540
Just relax. Come on.

608
00:54:43.015 --> 00:54:43.780
Let's sit down.

609
00:55:23.008 --> 00:55:24.258
Okay. Willie.

610
00:55:24.283 --> 00:55:25.783
Let me show you the stuff.

611
00:55:46.484 --> 00:55:47.940
Very good.

612
00:55:49.135 --> 00:55:49.940
Yes!

613
00:55:50.768 --> 00:55:51.740
Okay. Willie.

614
00:55:51.955 --> 00:55:53.421
Come on. I'll take you home.

615
00:55:53.977 --> 00:55:55.420
Caiwan Road. come on.

616
00:56:06.431 --> 00:56:07.904
Officer Luo. need help?

617
00:56:07.929 --> 00:56:09.430
Just mind your own business.

618
00:56:23.774 --> 00:56:24.283
Willie.

619
00:56:25.750 --> 00:56:26.740
We've got the money.

620
00:56:27.313 --> 00:56:28.260
Give my regards to your boss.

621
00:56:28.622 --> 00:56:29.788
See you next time.

622
00:56:29.813 --> 00:56:30.820
We have agreed.

623
00:56:31.318 --> 00:56:33.101
Very good. Good quality.

624
00:56:35.560 --> 00:56:37.439
Police! Take the boss away!

625
00:56:39.560 --> 00:56:41.810
- Raise your hands!
- Do not move!

626
00:57:06.902 --> 00:57:07.779
Song Bang.

627
00:57:36.074 --> 00:57:37.013
ADDRESS: CAIWAN STREET
COORDINATES: 48°N. 2°17'E

628
00:57:37.038 --> 00:57:37.555
TIME: 16:52

629
00:57:37.893 --> 00:57:39.100
It is time...

630
00:57:40.002 --> 00:57:41.020
...Officer Zheng.

631
00:57:45.248 --> 00:57:46.020
Za.

632
00:58:30.848 --> 00:58:31.890
Come on!

633
00:58:58.174 --> 00:59:00.540
Son. this time you work well.

634
00:59:02.926 --> 00:59:04.259
He's your boss.

635
00:59:04.287 --> 00:59:05.263
THREE DAYS BEFORE

636
00:59:05.288 --> 00:59:06.900
He has worked for me for years.

637
00:59:07.301 --> 00:59:08.500
Now you tell me
is he an undercover cop?

638
00:59:14.715 --> 00:59:16.060
Then I will definitely
wrong about him.

639
00:59:17.220 --> 00:59:18.660
If what I say is not true...

640
00:59:21.589 --> 00:59:22.940
...you can kill me.

641
00:59:25.344 --> 00:59:26.860
But if I'm right...

642
00:59:27.927 --> 00:59:29.300
...we will all die.

643
00:59:37.367 --> 00:59:39.700
Kid. you're not seasick. are you?

644
00:59:41.936 --> 00:59:45.140
No. I grew up
at the floating market.

645
00:59:46.593 --> 00:59:47.620
Is it true?

646
01:01:13.736 --> 01:01:15.820
Good people deserve
get good things.

647
01:01:43.928 --> 01:01:45.646
<i>Ten years ago.
you didn't kill me.</i>

648
01:01:45.988 --> 01:01:47.500
<i>I was returning the favor.</i>

649
01:01:47.948 --> 01:01:49.340
<i>But Song Bang must die.</i>

650
01:01:49.889 --> 01:01:51.599
<i>Live a good life with Zina.</i>

651
01:01:51.770 --> 01:01:52.780
<i>Don't look for me anymore.</i>

652
01:01:54.171 --> 01:01:55.820
That was my father's old boat.

653
01:01:59.792 --> 01:02:02.272
<i>- Hi. Za.</i>
- Eka Vat-Nava.

654
01:02:02.358 --> 01:02:04.780
What kind of boat is that?
Where is the boat anchored?

655
01:02:05.726 --> 01:02:07.684
<i>Eka Vat-Nava.</i>

656
01:02:07.709 --> 01:02:09.292
<i>Eka Pier.</i>

657
01:02:37.889 --> 01:02:38.740
Su Wan...

658
01:02:40.660 --> 01:02:41.700
...What do you want?

659
01:02:44.688 --> 01:02:45.900
Do you remember it?

660
01:02:48.922 --> 01:02:49.940
No.

661
01:02:50.794 --> 01:02:52.020
Can you give me a hint?

662
01:02:53.719 --> 01:02:54.900
Her name is Su Tai.

663
01:03:02.318 --> 01:03:03.943
You are careless.

664
01:03:05.938 --> 01:03:08.105
Dad. when
will your work be finished?

665
01:03:10.070 --> 01:03:12.300
Around noon. Then I
will come back to accompany you.

666
01:03:13.685 --> 01:03:14.220
Be nice.

667
01:03:14.843 --> 01:03:17.245
- Chief Su Tai. we have arrived.
- Hi. friends.

668
01:03:17.270 --> 01:03:18.220
Head!

669
01:03:20.222 --> 01:03:21.622
Head!

670
01:03:48.380 --> 01:03:49.460
<i>Su Tai.</i>

671
01:03:50.781 --> 01:03:52.006
Su Wan.

672
01:03:56.577 --> 01:03:59.180
So. you're the one who disappeared
ten years ago.

673
01:04:07.129 --> 01:04:09.796
Ten years ago. you killed him...

674
01:04:10.592 --> 01:04:12.092
...then throw it into the sea.

675
01:04:14.071 --> 01:04:17.488
I will make sure you meet him
in the same way.

676
01:04:20.284 --> 01:04:23.909
Are you ready to be
shark food. Mr. Song?

677
01:04:29.021 --> 01:04:30.340
What are you doing?

678
01:04:32.325 --> 01:04:33.950
Just makes you bleed a little.

679
01:04:34.429 --> 01:04:35.461
Become fishing bait.

680
01:04:49.897 --> 01:04:50.940
Don't kill him.

681
01:04:51.771 --> 01:04:53.271
He will go to jail.

682
01:04:57.815 --> 01:04:59.233
He has killed so many people.

683
01:04:59.353 --> 01:05:00.687
Has he ever been punished?

684
01:05:00.899 --> 01:05:02.140
I can catch it now.

685
01:05:02.313 --> 01:05:03.522
For all crimes
what he has done...

686
01:05:03.547 --> 01:05:05.220
...does he deserve it?
rot in prison?

687
01:05:05.812 --> 01:05:07.103
And you...

688
01:05:07.308 --> 01:05:08.804
...after working undercover
for years...

689
01:05:08.829 --> 01:05:10.121
...have you ever caught it?

690
01:05:10.321 --> 01:05:13.862
Even if you ever.
will he be punished?

691
01:05:20.125 --> 01:05:22.980
Death of your family
not a reason for revenge.

692
01:05:23.487 --> 01:05:25.737
That's because it's not
your deceased family.

693
01:06:06.406 --> 01:06:09.317
- Hello?
<i>- Dad is gone this week.</i>

694
01:06:09.431 --> 01:06:10.931
<i>When is Dad coming home?</i>

695
01:06:11.096 --> 01:06:12.060
<i>Let me talk to him.</i>

696
01:06:12.520 --> 01:06:13.936
<i>Why Dad?
not answering the phone?</i>

697
01:06:14.121 --> 01:06:16.205
<i>In addition. one continues
call our house.</i>

698
01:06:16.230 --> 01:06:17.620
I hear you.

699
01:06:18.615 --> 01:06:20.020
Okay. I'll take care of it.

700
01:06:21.722 --> 01:06:22.580
Don't worry.

701
01:06:24.059 --> 01:06:24.660
<i>Good.</i>

702
01:06:36.376 --> 01:06:37.360
Hello?

703
01:06:37.881 --> 01:06:39.091
<i>It's me.</i>

704
01:06:39.277 --> 01:06:40.900
Where are you?

705
01:06:41.225 --> 01:06:43.476
<i>We've been looking for you
everywhere.</i>

706
01:06:44.304 --> 01:06:45.377
I've caught Song Bang.

707
01:06:51.145 --> 01:06:52.060
You are okay?

708
01:06:53.175 --> 01:06:54.620
Meet me at Eka Pier first.

709
01:06:55.119 --> 01:06:56.244
<i>I'm on my way there.</i>

710
01:06:56.443 --> 01:06:57.695
<i>Our men will arrive later.</i>

711
01:06:59.630 --> 01:07:02.860
I have a tarnished witness here.
Can you take care of it?

712
01:07:04.322 --> 01:07:05.460
<i>What is the request?</i>

713
01:07:06.357 --> 01:07:07.420
Protection.

714
01:07:08.410 --> 01:07:09.660
Does anyone else know?

715
01:07:10.335 --> 01:07:11.335
<i>No.</i>

716
01:07:12.304 --> 01:07:14.179
<i>Okay. Wait for me.</i>

717
01:07:24.190 --> 01:07:25.700
What are your plans after this?

718
01:07:27.016 --> 01:07:29.301
Going to sea and fishing.

719
01:07:30.429 --> 01:07:32.700
Then I'll come along.

720
01:07:58.265 --> 01:07:59.660
- Where is he?
- Officer Luo.

721
01:08:01.394 --> 01:08:02.180
Song Bang.

722
01:08:08.804 --> 01:08:09.620
Then he?

723
01:08:11.096 --> 01:08:13.580
Her name is Su Wan.
My informant.

724
01:08:14.538 --> 01:08:15.820
Let him go.

725
01:08:29.634 --> 01:08:32.092
Mr. Song. why did you want to see me?

726
01:08:32.331 --> 01:08:33.700
I need your help.

727
01:08:34.829 --> 01:08:38.140
My job is to catch you.
not helping you.

728
01:08:39.047 --> 01:08:42.246
But I'm sure you don't
will disappoint me.

729
01:08:44.980 --> 01:08:46.732
MATTHEW KANE BIOGRAPHY

730
01:08:46.757 --> 01:08:49.882
Catch the dealer
This drug is easy for you.

731
01:08:50.045 --> 01:08:55.045
After that I will improve myself.
serving the community...

732
01:08:55.070 --> 01:08:58.612
...and repent.
all of that is also easy to do.

733
01:08:58.743 --> 01:08:59.909
It depends on the judge.

734
01:08:59.988 --> 01:09:01.072
The judge didn't know he was a criminal.

735
01:09:01.144 --> 01:09:02.500
I will look for evidence.

736
01:09:05.003 --> 01:09:06.500
What if you can't?

737
01:09:10.198 --> 01:09:13.540
You invested in property and lost.
You owe the bank a lot of money. I know.

738
01:09:14.236 --> 01:09:17.361
I also know the existence
the drug dealer.

739
01:09:18.460 --> 01:09:23.820
If you help me catch him.
I will pay off your debt.

740
01:09:25.849 --> 01:09:28.660
Then if I become mayor...

741
01:09:29.178 --> 01:09:31.119
...you will be promoted
become a commissioner.

742
01:09:34.842 --> 01:09:36.300
I won't help you.

743
01:09:38.072 --> 01:09:40.420
Try standing on a high place...

744
01:09:41.217 --> 01:09:44.540
...and look down. like me.

745
01:09:45.121 --> 01:09:49.140
The world looks different from above...

746
01:09:49.989 --> 01:09:51.526
...Commissioner.

747
01:10:03.746 --> 01:10:06.020
That is right.
Keep following me.

748
01:10:07.261 --> 01:10:08.419
Climb higher.

749
01:10:09.523 --> 01:10:10.660
Higher.

750
01:10:11.516 --> 01:10:12.740
Even higher.

751
01:10:13.459 --> 01:10:16.380
Higher. Good.
Getting higher.

752
01:10:17.996 --> 01:10:21.780
We will climb easily.

753
01:10:39.669 --> 01:10:40.549
Why?

754
01:10:40.715 --> 01:10:42.380
Be quiet.

755
01:10:44.145 --> 01:10:48.380
From now on there is no mafia or
drug dealer named Song Bang.

756
01:10:50.515 --> 01:10:52.940
I have completed your mission.

757
01:11:00.360 --> 01:11:04.152
Just made me some bait.

758
01:11:06.667 --> 01:11:09.900
I will make one for you too.
One more stab.

759
01:11:14.941 --> 01:11:16.580
All this time you were with me...

760
01:11:18.526 --> 01:11:23.940
...but you don't learn
to trust no one...

761
01:11:26.118 --> 01:11:27.180
...except yourself.

762
01:11:30.964 --> 01:11:31.780
Where is the item?

763
01:11:32.761 --> 01:11:34.340
In the evidence warehouse.

764
01:11:34.793 --> 01:11:36.460
Will be returned after being recorded.

765
01:11:37.549 --> 01:11:38.220
Give me the phone.

766
01:11:42.950 --> 01:11:44.660
It's me. Mr. Jin.

767
01:11:45.990 --> 01:11:47.620
What? Explanation?

768
01:11:48.452 --> 01:11:51.380
The item is missing
and my men died.

769
01:11:52.170 --> 01:11:56.420
The police are on your trail.
I also asked for an explanation.

770
01:11:59.709 --> 01:12:00.900
Do you want the item?

771
01:12:02.345 --> 01:12:04.820
I'll think about it.
See you later.

772
01:12:10.870 --> 01:12:14.900
The item is only worth 15 million
but I need 30 million.

773
01:12:16.377 --> 01:12:18.220
I have to sell it again.

774
01:12:21.391 --> 01:12:22.540
My initial plan...

775
01:12:24.105 --> 01:12:26.067
...finish you and Willie...

776
01:12:26.895 --> 01:12:28.660
...and let the police
confiscated my stuff.

777
01:12:30.214 --> 01:12:32.420
So there is no
who knows I betrayed.

778
01:12:34.824 --> 01:12:36.300
Who would have thought
this bastard would appear.

779
01:12:37.252 --> 01:12:41.020
Fortunately. there are only
one winner.

780
01:12:43.533 --> 01:12:45.060
That is me.

781
01:12:50.023 --> 01:12:51.580
What if it were like this?

782
01:12:52.117 --> 01:12:55.220
This is the first time.
never happened before.

783
01:12:55.781 --> 01:13:00.020
I will burn incense for you
while you are still alive.

784
01:13:01.380 --> 01:13:04.380
For you too for you.

785
01:13:05.844 --> 01:13:08.300
Hopefully we don't meet again.

786
01:14:45.959 --> 01:14:49.834
ONE MONTH LATER

787
01:15:16.629 --> 01:15:18.209
You've been lying down
for more than a month.

788
01:15:18.613 --> 01:15:21.060
The doctor said your muscles
experiencing severe atrophy.

789
01:15:22.469 --> 01:15:25.100
Your vocal cords and throat
also suffered serious injuries.

790
01:15:27.393 --> 01:15:28.500
Take it easy.

791
01:15:32.891 --> 01:15:35.381
Your face is badly burned.
Cannot be returned.

792
01:15:36.494 --> 01:15:39.660
Before he died. Zha wanted to
you got a face donor.

793
01:15:40.494 --> 01:15:42.758
Live a good life
with the identity of Zha.

794
01:15:50.862 --> 01:15:53.900
I've tried my best.
but he didn't survive.

795
01:15:59.023 --> 01:15:59.860
See for yourself.

796
01:16:00.770 --> 01:16:05.660
<i>Polls show
Song Bang leads in the northern area.</i>

797
01:16:13.600 --> 01:16:16.820
<i>You have received your final payment
and your home is now safe.</i>

798
01:16:17.029 --> 01:16:18.300
<i>What about your promise to me?</i>

799
01:16:18.609 --> 01:16:21.900
Do not worry.
Your goods will be delivered tomorrow.

800
01:16:22.643 --> 01:16:24.980
Tomorrow. we will break even.

801
01:16:25.353 --> 01:16:29.353
<i>Come on. our deal not just once.</i>

802
01:16:29.478 --> 01:16:31.460
<i>Now we are partners.</i>

803
01:16:31.852 --> 01:16:35.374
<i>I will make you a commissioner.</i>

804
01:16:35.735 --> 01:16:37.820
<i>Tomorrow I'm counting on you.</i>

805
01:16:39.515 --> 01:16:42.889
<i>Mr. Song. your belongings are secured.
from the destruction site...</i>

806
01:16:42.914 --> 01:16:44.060
<i>...and has been submitted
to your men.</i>

807
01:16:44.314 --> 01:16:45.880
FUNDS IN
AS MUCH AS 15.000.000 USD

808
01:16:47.709 --> 01:16:48.660
How?

809
01:16:49.976 --> 01:16:53.340
Okay. I promise
this is the last transaction.

810
01:16:54.235 --> 01:16:55.300
May your business be successful.

811
01:18:01.147 --> 01:18:02.479
OPEN

812
01:18:02.504 --> 01:18:03.766
CLOSED

813
01:19:00.635 --> 01:19:02.500
Sorry. sir. we are closed.

814
01:19:07.123 --> 01:19:09.821
Closed tonight or forever?

815
01:19:11.401 --> 01:19:12.940
We are closed this month.

816
01:19:23.022 --> 01:19:28.140
From now on. there will be no more
who knows his identity.

817
01:19:28.301 --> 01:19:29.591
PERSONNEL NOTES
POLICE DEPARTMENT

818
01:19:30.581 --> 01:19:32.159
Zheng Zha has a girlfriend.

819
01:19:36.406 --> 01:19:37.823
He doesn't know anything.

820
01:19:37.848 --> 01:19:39.500
I didn't ask for your opinion.

821
01:19:45.609 --> 01:19:46.380
Excuse me.

822
01:19:48.090 --> 01:19:49.260
Song Bang wants you dead.

823
01:19:50.264 --> 01:19:53.914
Blame yourself
because he knew Zheng Zha.

824
01:20:02.481 --> 01:20:03.660
Zheng Zha?

825
01:20:05.322 --> 01:20:06.489
Listen to me.

826
01:20:06.769 --> 01:20:07.780
I was forced to do this.

827
01:20:08.132 --> 01:20:09.460
This is not my fault.

828
01:20:11.167 --> 01:20:12.976
Absolutely not.
You have to trust me.

829
01:20:13.041 --> 01:20:14.221
I don't...

830
01:20:17.853 --> 01:20:19.185
You want to catch Song Bang. right?

831
01:20:19.461 --> 01:20:20.860
I have the proof.

832
01:20:21.841 --> 01:20:23.716
The proof is on my phone.

833
01:20:23.781 --> 01:20:24.989
I can help you.

834
01:20:25.210 --> 01:20:26.543
Don't kill me.

835
01:20:29.054 --> 01:20:30.763
I will help you catch Song Bang.

836
01:20:30.997 --> 01:20:32.831
I am willing to be a witness.

837
01:20:33.420 --> 01:20:34.962
I want to go to jail
if required.

838
01:20:35.001 --> 01:20:36.333
Just don't kill me.

839
01:20:36.458 --> 01:20:38.082
I can help your career
restored again.

840
01:20:38.391 --> 01:20:41.184
Only I can prove your identity
as an undercover police officer.

841
01:20:41.213 --> 01:20:42.839
After your name is restored...

842
01:20:42.864 --> 01:20:44.420
...you can take my position.

843
01:20:46.201 --> 01:20:48.700
Hey. you are a police officer.

844
01:20:48.999 --> 01:20:50.940
You can't kill me.

845
01:21:33.767 --> 01:21:34.460
Zha..

846
01:21:35.953 --> 01:21:37.380
Thank you for
taking care of me all this time.

847
01:21:39.555 --> 01:21:40.460
I will give my respect...

848
01:21:41.595 --> 01:21:42.860
...for you with
this glass of arak.

849
01:21:46.219 --> 01:21:46.980
Be careful.

850
01:21:53.942 --> 01:21:54.962
Everything is ready.

851
01:21:55.495 --> 01:21:56.362
There is a ship...

852
01:21:56.767 --> 01:21:58.620
...from Pengjiang Wharf to Africa
South at 8:00 AM tomorrow.

853
01:21:59.940 --> 01:22:01.260
You go or stay here...

854
01:22:02.196 --> 01:22:03.300
...up to you.

855
01:22:05.033 --> 01:22:06.341
I will pretend that
I never saw you.

856
01:22:23.902 --> 01:22:25.569
Come here. check this out.

857
01:22:26.035 --> 01:22:28.201
Officer Mai. CCTV cameras recorded...

858
01:22:28.228 --> 01:22:29.940
...a man goes
with pregnant women.

859
01:22:30.480 --> 01:22:31.772
- Check it out.
- Good.

860
01:22:32.253 --> 01:22:35.462
Check the airport. docks.
train station. bus terminal...

861
01:22:35.674 --> 01:22:36.740
...and the maternity ward
in the hospital.

862
01:22:37.493 --> 01:22:38.743
Look for them at all costs.

863
01:22:39.016 --> 01:22:40.820
- Okay sir.
- Wait.

864
01:22:42.037 --> 01:22:43.331
- This needs to be checked.
- Go to the Intelligence Department.

865
01:22:43.835 --> 01:22:45.085
And cross-check the data.

866
01:22:45.517 --> 01:22:46.100
Yes. Sir.

867
01:22:50.556 --> 01:22:51.660
There's blood here.

868
01:23:04.125 --> 01:23:06.823
Today. Song Bang.
mayoral candidate...

869
01:23:06.848 --> 01:23:07.950
...for Mancheng Laika...

870
01:23:08.107 --> 01:23:11.524
<i>...attend the send-off ceremony
New Year at Sunan River.</i>

871
01:23:11.902 --> 01:23:13.213
<i>He gave an offering
for all city residents.</i>

872
01:23:14.180 --> 01:23:15.225
<i>Residents expressed their hopes...</i>

873
01:23:15.250 --> 01:23:17.749
<i>...for Song Bang's leadership.</i>

874
01:23:17.952 --> 01:23:22.060
<i>Residents believe he can lead
Mancheng to a bright future.</i>

875
01:23:22.691 --> 01:23:25.660
Thank you very much!

876
01:23:25.961 --> 01:23:27.653
Thank You!

877
01:23:34.808 --> 01:23:35.620
Don't shoot.

878
01:23:36.778 --> 01:23:37.633
There are too many people here.

879
01:23:41.009 --> 01:23:43.310
The fish is strange.
He has been released into the water...

880
01:23:43.335 --> 01:23:44.420
...but he jumped back onto land.
looking for death.

881
01:23:47.082 --> 01:23:48.660
There are too many people here.
Don't make a fuss.

882
01:23:49.284 --> 01:23:50.180
Wait for me at my hotel.

883
01:23:54.264 --> 01:23:55.889
<i>Song Bang will not let us go.</i>

884
01:23:57.034 --> 01:23:58.113
<i>Just go to the hospital.</i>

885
01:23:59.268 --> 01:24:00.727
<i>If I could go back...</i>

886
01:24:01.191 --> 01:24:02.580
<i>...I will pick you up.</i>

887
01:24:04.136 --> 01:24:05.928
<i>Zha gave that name to the child.</i>

888
01:24:06.319 --> 01:24:07.340
<i>Remember.</i>

889
01:25:13.079 --> 01:25:15.589
PERSONNEL BIODATA
LAIKA POLICE

890
01:25:18.717 --> 01:25:21.404
DATA RECOVERY

891
01:25:23.596 --> 01:25:24.846
<i>Don't worry.</i>

892
01:25:25.417 --> 01:25:27.292
<i>The goods will be shipped
handed over to you tomorrow.</i>

893
01:25:27.323 --> 01:25:30.988
<i>I will prepare the position
commissioner for you.</i>

894
01:25:31.357 --> 01:25:32.681
Officer Mai. we have intelligence.

895
01:25:32.706 --> 01:25:33.940
Zheng Zha went to Song's house.

896
01:25:34.660 --> 01:25:36.201
- Let's move.
- Okay sir!

897
01:31:04.416 --> 01:31:05.749
Push.

898
01:31:06.779 --> 01:31:08.112
Good.

899
01:31:08.692 --> 01:31:10.011
Again. Push harder.

900
01:31:10.036 --> 01:31:11.714
The situation is very critical.

901
01:31:11.739 --> 01:31:13.049
If you insist
giving birth naturally...

902
01:31:13.074 --> 01:31:14.350
...your life will be in danger.

903
01:31:14.375 --> 01:31:15.709
Breathe!

904
01:31:16.125 --> 01:31:16.660
Good.

905
01:31:16.885 --> 01:31:19.135
- Push again.
- Please save..

906
01:31:19.761 --> 01:31:20.447
Save..

907
01:31:20.483 --> 01:31:20.860
Push.

908
01:31:20.885 --> 01:31:22.934
- Save the child..
- Push again!

909
01:31:22.959 --> 01:31:27.100
- You have to save..
- Zheng Yi.

910
01:31:57.073 --> 01:32:00.180
Officer Zheng. are you looking for me?

911
01:32:28.432 --> 01:32:29.900
You are really great.

912
01:32:31.958 --> 01:32:34.180
You can get here alone.

913
01:32:35.959 --> 01:32:36.940
But what a shame.

914
01:32:37.375 --> 01:32:38.420
The police will be here soon.

915
01:32:38.875 --> 01:32:39.980
They will see...

916
01:32:40.468 --> 01:32:41.800
...a crazy intruder
breaking into the house...

917
01:32:42.158 --> 01:32:43.908
...a mayoral candidate.

918
01:32:43.933 --> 01:32:44.860
Then...

919
01:32:45.657 --> 01:32:48.180
...shot by Mayor Song.

920
01:32:49.496 --> 01:32:50.860
Tomorrow the newspaper will say...

921
01:32:51.613 --> 01:32:53.980
...political rivals are suspected
in the attack on Song."

922
01:32:56.433 --> 01:32:57.660
Thank you for your help.

923
01:33:14.239 --> 01:33:14.860
Why?

924
01:33:16.406 --> 01:33:17.300
You refuse to die?

925
01:33:19.182 --> 01:33:21.100
You are indeed tough.

926
01:33:28.517 --> 01:33:29.940
I recognize the handle of this knife.

927
01:33:31.055 --> 01:33:33.340
Isn't it made of sacred wood?
the one you took 10 years ago?

928
01:33:34.015 --> 01:33:34.780
Too bad.

929
01:33:35.995 --> 01:33:37.700
Even God will not
protect you now.

930
01:33:40.082 --> 01:33:41.083
Does not matter.

931
01:33:41.585 --> 01:33:43.060
I will send you to the afterlife.

932
01:33:58.420 --> 01:34:00.140
Zheng Zha. drop the weapon!

933
01:34:00.895 --> 01:34:03.021
Shoot him!
He's going to kill me!

934
01:34:03.313 --> 01:34:04.939
I'm going to die!
Shoot him now!

935
01:34:04.964 --> 01:34:05.965
Zheng Zha!

936
01:34:06.195 --> 01:34:08.029
Your police number is PC4489.

937
01:34:08.079 --> 01:34:09.301
You report directly to Luo En.

938
01:34:10.004 --> 01:34:11.740
I have recovered
all data from Luo En's phone.

939
01:34:17.875 --> 01:34:18.900
Zheng Zha!

940
01:34:22.208 --> 01:34:23.751
I'm not Zheng Zha.

941
01:35:48.497 --> 01:35:49.536
PLEASE CALM

942
01:35:49.561 --> 01:35:50.610
WASH YOUR HANDS
AS OFTEN AS POSSIBLE

943
01:36:00.623 --> 01:36:01.340
Mr. Song.

944
01:36:02.150 --> 01:36:03.982
Zheng Zha tries to attack you.

945
01:36:04.085 --> 01:36:06.044
You pull out a gun
to defend oneself.

946
01:36:06.076 --> 01:36:07.220
They can't sue you for it.

947
01:36:09.597 --> 01:36:10.820
We must believe in the law.

948
01:36:11.694 --> 01:36:13.780
The law protects
good people like us...

949
01:36:14.442 --> 01:36:17.104
...and make sure not to
there are bad guys who got away.

950
01:36:17.129 --> 01:36:19.047
- Do you understand?
- You are right.

951
01:36:19.083 --> 01:36:21.083
From now on.
leave everything to me.

952
01:36:21.108 --> 01:36:23.275
You don't need to answer
anyone's question.

953
01:38:07.154 --> 01:38:08.487
I apologize.

954
01:38:10.941 --> 01:38:12.340
Thank You.

955
01:38:15.069 --> 01:38:17.060
This is for you.

956
01:38:43.955 --> 01:38:45.340
TRANSLATION: MNC VISION
